      &lt;img class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;https://localhost:1313/assets/images/wiapost/5171-Awareness-And-Consciousness.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Awareness and Consciousness&#34; /&gt;
      
